flowchart LR
    subgraph INPUT[Input]
        A[User Profile Source<br/>target mood, genre, energy, tempo, acoustic preference]
        B[Song Dataset Source<br/>docs/data/songs.json + docs/data/profiles.json]
    end

    subgraph CORE[AI Recommendation Pipeline]
        C[Feature Retriever]
        D[Scoring Agent<br/>mood distance, energy difference,<br/>genre flags, tempo difference, acoustic match]
        E[Feedback Integrator<br/>seed feedback + live likes and skips]
        F[Evaluator and Guardrails<br/>confidence and score-spread checks]
    end

    subgraph OUTPUT[Output]
        G[Top 5 Recommendations<br/>scores + explanations]
    end

    A --> C
    B --> C
    C --> D --> E --> F --> G

    G -->|shown to user| H
    H[Human User] -->|Like or Skip| E
    T[Testing Layer<br/>manual checks + pytest] -->|validates ranking behavior| F
